folder: Oxford Street N. & Park Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
original_title: Brooklyn: Oxford Street N. - Park Avenue
text:
North Oxford Street, north from (No. 31) a point midway between Park and Flushing Avenues, toward the latter, showing a W. P. A. sewer project. In the background is the Brooklyn Navy Yard.

August 7, 1935

Works Progress Administration
Five Boroughs Project
